tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE trade_history (
    trade_id INT,
    symbol VARCHAR(10),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    volume INT,
    trade_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE trades (
    trade_id INT,
    stock_id INT,
    strategy_id INT,
    trade_type VARCHAR,
    trade_volume INT
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id INT,
    trade_id INT,
    order_type VARCHAR,
    order_price FLOAT,
    order_status VARCHAR
);
